{"tid":639392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩先試完番梘水射曱甴！堅work！","createTime":"2018-04-23T12:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T16:24:22.000Z","uid":29314,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"080838222816b92cdde70a4cb6d0049de951a18f","tid":639392,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:20:39.000Z","msg":"幾秒隻曱甴就唔識郁！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原理：「用肥皂水殺曱甴，一定要對準曱甴身體，最好噴到腹部，只要肥皂水分量足，可去掉曱甴身體表面的蠟質、油質，堵住曱甴氣門，令曱甴窒息而死；若只噴到曱甴背部，如果肥皂水分量足夠，流到腹部就會發揮作用。」"},{"pid":"9dcc4b9860d71a0de441a7c24466c0037bceead1","tid":639392,"uid":4826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"冇圖？"},{"pid":"3488fa191809c908309f60cfc108f37c9a3909db","tid":639392,"uid":144774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"試過work"},{"pid":"fdccd94ac87e801af570e958138f0f56c424bdee","tid":639392,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:24:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇圖？</blockquote><br />\n無圖。<br />\n<br />\n可以文字描述：<br />\n<br />\n用番梘泡tart落曱甴度。效果顯著！"},{"pid":"26d3ccbcab22e934581e5546290e2cbe91873201","tid":639392,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:25:55.000Z","msg":"萬潔靈。快過殺蟲劑"},{"pid":"0b2c4357cf675eacd98cdc6131b2d9749fd0e4d4","tid":639392,"uid":156121,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"洗潔精最快<br />\n好過殺蟲水 一中鹼水就唔識郁"},{"pid":"c1320446c93383ea860ebdd28d3b468b9af8425d","tid":639392,"uid":31733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"一早試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faeea1fa6490feb119f17df32342af5c0db94eb1","tid":639392,"uid":46900,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:37:13.000Z","msg":"揾得啲野黎隻野已經消失佐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f983714ed94e8e29fc8f49e09bbb9cd